==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lingering
<hw>Lin"ger*ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Delaying.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Drawn out in time; remaining long; protracted;
<as>as, a <ex>lingering</ex> disease</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To die is the fate of man; but to die with <qex>lingering</qex>
anguish is generally his folly.</q> <rj><qau>Rambler.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lingeringly</ent>⟦br⟧
